# Unity Scene Files
# =================
# This folder contains Unity scene files for the game.
#
# Available Scenes:
# -----------------
# - MainMenu.unity - Main menu with Start Game and Quit buttons
# - MainGame.unity - Main gameplay scene (to be created in Unity Editor)
#
# Scene Setup Notes:
# ------------------
# MainMenu Scene:
# - Contains MainMenuCanvas with Start Game and Quit buttons
# - MainMenuUI script handles button click events
# - GameManager singleton manages scene transitions
#
# To add scenes to build:
# 1. Open File > Build Settings in Unity
# 2. Add MainMenu and MainGame scenes
# 3. Ensure MainMenu is scene index 0
